headline: Alliant Energy (LNT) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Alliant Energy (LNT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 45.61% and 0.17%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
